data.description: The stunning Reed plan is a new four-bedroom home at Quarter Horse Estates. This spacious single-story home has a large, open family room paired with a chef-ready kitchen and luxurious master suite. Inside the Reed, you’ll find incredible included upgrades such as granite countertops, energy-efficient kitchen appliances, luxury vinyl-plank flooring, a Wi-F-enabled garage door opener and more. Schedule your tour of the Reed plan at Quarter Horse Estates today!
